# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:4
translate chinese graduation_fcda8f21:

    # "That weekend, the time has come. I'm finally going to graduate."
    "那个周末，终于到了。我终于要毕业了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:7
translate chinese graduation_9322fbe2:

    # "I'm pretty nervous. Not for the walking across the stage, but for what comes after."
    "我有点紧张。不是因为走上舞台，而是因为之后的事情。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:8
translate chinese graduation_b5eb6fe8:

    # "I'm going to have to make a lot of decisions."
    "我得做出很多决定。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:9
translate chinese graduation_3c7f2f57:

    # "What career path I'm going to take."
    "我该走哪条职业道路。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:10
translate chinese graduation_292aaa1a:

    # "Where I'm going to live."
    "我要住在哪里。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:11
translate chinese graduation_6f7a21ba:

    # "And most importantly..."
    "最重要的是……"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:12
translate chinese graduation_6dec3447:

    # "... who I'm going to be with."
    "……我要和谁在一起。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:15
translate chinese graduation_bb5d5c1b:

    # "I see Jamie graduate. She looks so happy. Her dad cheers for her in the audience."
    "我看着杰米毕业。她看起来那么开心。她的爸爸在观众席上为她欢呼。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:16
translate chinese graduation_ddb94435:

    # "I wonder who is here to cheer for me."
    "我好奇，这里有没有人为我欢呼。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:19
translate chinese graduation_c59ac221:

    # "When it's my turn, I walk across the stage to take my diploma."
    "轮到我时，我走上舞台领取毕业证书。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:21
translate chinese graduation_43c2c1fd:

    # "I hear a roar of applause and cheering from the crowd."
    "我听到人群中爆发出雷鸣般的掌声和欢呼声。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:23
translate chinese graduation_ba624ddd:

    # "I hear people in the audience applauding and cheering for me."
    "我听到观众席里有人为我鼓掌欢呼。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:25
translate chinese graduation_50c87cd2:

    # "I hear a few claps and cheers from the audience."
    "我听到观众席里传来零星的掌声和欢呼声。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:27
translate chinese graduation_dc5c5344:

    # "The audience is embarrassingly quiet. I don't hear anybody cheering for me."
    "观众席里安静得令人尴尬。我听不到有人为我欢呼。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:65
translate chinese graduation_a1216c7c:

    # "I look out and see my cheering section in the audience and give them a wave."
    "我环顾四周，看到观众席里为我加油的亲友团，便向他们挥了挥手。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:68
translate chinese graduation_379ce65b:

    # "The dean shakes my hand and gives me my diploma."
    "院长与我握手，并将毕业证书交到我手中。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:69
translate chinese graduation_185e2b9c:

    # "I don't think I've ever met him before, but he looks so familiar."
    "我好像从未见过他，但他看起来却如此眼熟。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:72
translate chinese graduation_48469141:

    # "I can't believe I did it. Even with all the other things going on..."
    "我简直不敢相信自己做到了。即便经历了所有那些事情……"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:73
translate chinese graduation_ca6a8913:

    # "... I graduated college."
    "……我大学毕业了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:74
translate chinese graduation_464c98b1:

    # "It's a huge accomplishment."
    "这是一项巨大的成就。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:75
translate chinese graduation_9194429e:

    # "But now the real challenge begins. I have to live the rest of my life."
    "但真正的挑战才刚刚开始。我得去过完余生。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:79
translate chinese graduation_88f825fa:

    # "And I have to make a choice."
    "而且我必须做出选择。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:80
translate chinese graduation_35304928:

    # "After the ceremony finishes, I'm approached by people who want to congratulate me."
    "典礼结束后，不少人上前向我道贺。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:86
translate chinese graduation_1b8bc31b:

    # sp "I'm so proud of you, [pcname]."
    sp "[pcname]，我为你感到骄傲。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:87
translate chinese graduation_edf6ed48:

    # sp "I know your father would be too."
    sp "我知道你父亲也会为你骄傲的。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:91
translate chinese graduation_ac0c2fb4:

    # ss "Wow, [bro]. You actually graduated!"
    ss "哇，[bro]。你居然真的毕业了！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:92
translate chinese graduation_c8fc7fac:

    # ss "I'm so proud of you!"
    ss "我为你感到骄傲！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:93
translate chinese graduation_e7a915a9:

    # tm "Yeah, good job [pcname]! Glad you didn't lose too many brain cells in the ring with me."
    tm "是啊，干得漂亮，[pcname]！还好你跟我一起在拳台上没损失太多脑细胞。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:97
translate chinese graduation_c04f8b26:

    # cw "Congratulations, [pcname]. I knew you could do it. You're so smart."
    cw "恭喜你，[pcname]。我就知道你能行。你太聪明了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:101
translate chinese graduation_329f830b:

    # bs "Congratulations, [fuckboy]. Always knew you were smarter than you looked."
    bs "恭喜你，[fuckboy]。我一直觉得你比看起来要聪明。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:102
translate chinese graduation_f878f94a:

    # pc "Thanks, Mrs. Mills. Are you going to stay to celebrate?"
    pc "谢谢，米尔斯夫人。您要留下来庆祝吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:105
translate chinese graduation_3becdb7b:

    # bs "Nah, that's not for me. You have fun though."
    bs "不，那不适合我。不过你们玩得开心点。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:106
translate chinese graduation_2d81c45d:

    # bs "Seriously... I'm proud of you and I hope you get everything you want out of life."
    bs "说真的……我为你感到骄傲，希望你能实现人生的所有愿望。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:107
translate chinese graduation_4bd7bc94:

    # bs "Bye, [pcname]."
    bs "再见，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:112
translate chinese graduation_d62fed7f:

    # gnd "Can you believe we actually did it?"
    gnd "你能相信我们真的做到了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:113
translate chinese graduation_7af6eec9:

    # pc "Barely."
    pc "勉强算吧。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:114
translate chinese graduation_70db59f2:

    # gnd "Thanks for all your help. I'm happy I get to walk across the stage with my best friend."
    gnd "谢谢你的帮助。能和最好的朋友一起走上舞台，我真的很开心。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:118
translate chinese graduation_574568d3:

    # fr "Wow, [pcname]! You're a college graduate now!"
    fr "哇，[pcname]！你现在是大学毕业生了！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:119
translate chinese graduation_d4964952:

    # fr "I'm so proud of you!"
    fr "我为你感到无比自豪！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:123
translate chinese graduation_81a7f5e2:

    # et "Congratulations, [pcname]. You did a great job this year."
    et "恭喜你，[pcname]。你今年表现得非常棒。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:124
translate chinese graduation_2ff53a2d:

    # mrmg "Yeah, Edie and I are both very proud of you."
    mrmg "是啊，艾迪和我都很为你骄傲。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:125
translate chinese graduation_046748d2:

    # pc "Thanks, you two."
    pc "谢谢你们俩。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:128
translate chinese graduation_f61c3028:

    # mrmg "We're going to take off, but if you ever want to come by, feel free."
    mrmg "我们要走了，但如果你想来玩，随时欢迎。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:129
translate chinese graduation_d3a78723:

    # et "Bye, [pcname]. I hope to see you again soon."
    et "再见，[pcname]。希望很快能再见到你。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:134
translate chinese graduation_bece76e0:

    # bn "Congratulations, [pcname]! I'm happy that you were able to make it."
    bn "恭喜你，[pcname]！很高兴你最终做到了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:135
translate chinese graduation_73f0d30c:

    # pc "Not sure I could have done it without some help on those essays."
    pc "要不是那些论文有人帮忙，我可能做不到。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:136
translate chinese graduation_a995bba0:

    # bn "You really have improved a lot since then. I'm glad I could help."
    bn "你那之后真的进步了很多。能帮上忙我很高兴。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:140
translate chinese graduation_7379e0ab:

    # gl "Damn, Twig! You a college graduate now!"
    gl "天啊，Twig！你现在可是大学毕业生了！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:141
translate chinese graduation_4d0b6de5:

    # gl "That's pretty fuckin cool. Good job, man."
    gl "这简直太酷了。干得漂亮，老兄。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:145
translate chinese graduation_c1d7fd4b:

    # sg "Wow, congratulations! I knew you could do it."
    sg "哇，恭喜！我就知道你能行。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:146
translate chinese graduation_0cde929c:

    # sg "My [kdaddy] is super smart."
    sg "我的[kdaddy]超级聪明。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:150
translate chinese graduation_25ea1d82:

    # gg "Good job [pcname]! I'm really proud of you."
    gg "干得漂亮，[pcname]！我真的很为你骄傲。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:154
translate chinese graduation_9bb0179c:

    # sst "Congratulations, [pcname]. I've seen how bright you are and I know you'll accomplish big things."
    sst "恭喜你，[pcname]。我一直知道你很聪明，相信你将来定能成就一番大事业。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:155
translate chinese graduation_cf39cc04:

    # sst "Plus... I'm not your teacher anymore, so I'm looking forward to spending a {i}lot{/i} more time with you."
    sst "而且……我不再是你的老师了，所以很期待能有{i}更多{/i}时间陪你。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:159
translate chinese graduation_7758b810:

    # fd "Congratulations, [pcname]! What a big accomplishment."
    fd "恭喜你，[pcname]！真是了不起的成就。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:160
translate chinese graduation_e2fac1f5:

    # fd "So proud of you."
    fd "我为你感到无比自豪。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:164
translate chinese graduation_95a9907c:

    # rb "Dang, [pcname]! You graduated!"
    rb "天啊，[pcname]！你毕业了！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:165
translate chinese graduation_193230c7:

    # rb "I'm super proud of you. I hope I can do that one day too."
    rb "我为你超级自豪。希望有一天我也能做到。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:169
translate chinese graduation_3f04f91d:

    # wt "Congratulations, [pcname]. Now the real work begins."
    wt "恭喜你，[pcname]。现在真正的挑战才刚刚开始。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:173
translate chinese graduation_99a6a955:

    # bai "Congratulations, [pcname]! I'm very proud of you."
    bai "恭喜你，[pcname]！我为你感到非常自豪。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:177
translate chinese graduation_098f36f3:

    # det "Good job, [pcname]. I'm so proud of you."
    det "干得漂亮，[pcname]。我为你感到无比自豪。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:178
translate chinese graduation_ce2f89e3:

    # det "Plus, now I don't have to feel weird anymore about dating a guy who is still in school."
    det "而且，现在我再也不用因为和还在上学的男生约会而感到尴尬了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:182
translate chinese graduation_1af6aa31:

    # mc "Congratulations, [pcname]. You have made a huge accomplishment today."
    mc "恭喜你，[pcname]。今天你取得了巨大的成就。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:183
translate chinese graduation_8189962e:

    # mc "Just one more step on a long and successful life."
    mc "这只是你漫长而成功的人生中迈出的又一步。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:184
translate chinese graduation_e019ba6d:

    # mc "Oh I also wanted to tell you that Mrs. Spann has taken care of things. I do not have to go back to Korea until at least next year."
    mc "哦，我还想告诉你，斯潘夫人已经把事情处理好了。至少明年之前我都不用回韩国了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:185
translate chinese graduation_e73708a0:

    # pc "That's great!"
    pc "太好了！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:186
translate chinese graduation_aea2d457:

    # mc "Yes, I am very happy. I wanted you to know before you make your choice."
    mc "是的，我非常开心。我想在你做出决定之前让你知道这件事。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:190
translate chinese graduation_3251ea55:

    # sc "Congratulations, [pcname]. I knew you could do it."
    sc "恭喜你，[pcname]。我就知道你能行。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:191
translate chinese graduation_5ef55c33:

    # pc "Thanks, Gertrude. Are you going to stay to celebrate?"
    pc "谢谢，格特鲁德。你会留下来一起庆祝吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:194
translate chinese graduation_d43e5efb:

    # sc "I'm sorry, but no. I hope you have a great time though."
    sc "很抱歉，不行。不过希望你能玩得开心。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:195
translate chinese graduation_1d485803:

    # sc "I'm actually going to be leaving soon."
    sc "其实我马上就要走了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:196
translate chinese graduation_0d75ddc6:

    # pc "Leaving?"
    pc "要走了？"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:197
translate chinese graduation_5aba87b6:

    # sc "Yes, I'm going on a bit of a journey. But I'll keep in touch, I promise."
    sc "是的，我要去一段旅程。但我会保持联系的，我保证。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:200
translate chinese graduation_aaca6d60:

    # pc "Well, good luck. I hope you find what you're looking for... and I'll miss you."
    pc "那，祝你好运。希望你能找到你想要的……我会想你的。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:201
translate chinese graduation_55242658:

    # sc "I'll miss you too, [pcname]. Take care of yourself."
    sc "我也会想你的，[pcname]。保重。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:202
translate chinese graduation_6679f75b:

    # pc "Bye, Gertrude."
    pc "再见，格特鲁德。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:208
translate chinese graduation_ce23737e:

    # "So who do I want to celebrate with?"
    "那么，我想和谁一起庆祝呢？"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20graduation.rpy:209
translate chinese graduation_cbc63806:

    # "I guess it's time to make my choice."
    "我想是时候做出我的选择了。"

